Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.38,0:01:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.18,0:01:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我实现…我的愿望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.72,0:01:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不就像「黄泉归来」里的情节嘛!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.72,0:01:52.00,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}黄泉归来（黄泉がえり），梶尾真治的小说及同名电影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.97,0:01:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.67,0:01:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间为了让你实现她的愿望竟然会从黄泉归来!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.28,0:02:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不…我想那只是我所看见的幻想而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.08,0:02:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻想?你是说fantasy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.78,0:02:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.80,0:02:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在这里嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.17,0:02:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…现在不…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.97,0:02:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间! 是我啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.47,0:02:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.59,0:02:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.10,0:02:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪啊 芽间 露个脸嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.85,0:02:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑子一热就把芽间的事情全盘托出了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到他居然这么老实地就接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.83,0:02:22.50,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}芽间～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.74,0:02:24.95,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}芽间!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.12,0:02:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 我看不到她…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.52,0:02:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以都说是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.11,0:02:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳果然好厉害啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.09,0:02:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个秘密基地是你在用吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.18,0:02:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不过只是我在日本停留的时候用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.52,0:02:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在日本?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.33,0:02:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.46,0:02:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些红色的 就是我去过的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我想看遍世界各地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.63,0:02:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是打工攒钱 然后去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.16,0:02:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那高中怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.35,0:02:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种地方 我没空去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.77,0:03:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前我去东南亚走了一转
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.73,0:03:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越南的女人很可爱啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.67,0:03:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳好厉害!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.27,0:03:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前个子小小的 现在都长得熊一样大了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.32,0:03:11.46,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}像酱紫 酱紫～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.34,0:03:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:15.10,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}真是可爱得不行了啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.93,0:03:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是没有变…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.20,0:03:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.90,0:03:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变了很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.98,0:03:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来「森林探险」不?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:24.64,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}会有什么跑出来呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.06,0:03:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 跑题了跑题了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在说芽间的心愿吧 你们有过什么约定不?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没印象…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.57,0:03:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是不是说过想要仁碳你手里那个「就是撒」的签名?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:38.18,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}「就是撒（ですよ。）」，日本一搞笑艺人的艺名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她会专门为了「就是撒」而变鬼跑出来么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.21,0:03:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…是那个?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 栗丸你怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.03,0:04:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家后我会给你喝酸奶的啦 酸奶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.42,0:04:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.43,0:04:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣子啊 你还真的去宿海家了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.84,0:04:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.55,0:04:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得去找那家里蹲真是糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.27,0:04:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 但是啊 偶尔不也会这样嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.51,0:04:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.36,0:04:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 总觉得提不起劲 或是早上不想起床之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.53,0:04:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我偶尔也会…不 经常会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.70,0:04:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好啦 不过我才不想和那种阴暗的家伙相提并论呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他现在肯定在拿鸣子想一些色色的事情 一定的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.26,0:04:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 有可能～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.37,0:04:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恶心～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.08,0:05:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女人搞毛啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.48,0:05:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是王大附中的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.91,0:05:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贱货
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤见子?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.65,0:05:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.65,0:05:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.01,0:05:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢光临
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.31,0:05:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.77,0:05:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤见同学!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.90,0:05:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊 你忘东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.28,0:05:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种情况你放在那不管就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.24,0:05:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被别人看到我跟绿高的人说话 那得有多难堪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.97,0:05:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么意思啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.09,0:05:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.22,0:05:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家好心给你拿过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.40,0:05:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没求你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.14,0:05:57.00,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}不行不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.06,0:06:00.56,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}安鸣和鹤见子都是 别吵架啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.10,0:05:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么时候开始变得这么自傲的?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.63,0:06:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前可是一直都小心翼翼的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.30,0:06:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可真是一点没变
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.14,0:06:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前就一直容易被人影响
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 跟一起来的那些大腿都已经合不拢的女人一个模样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.09,0:06:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大腿?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.03,0:06:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还亏你以前一直在模仿着本间芽衣子的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.66,0:06:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不许你随便拿那死去的孩子的名字来说事!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.13,0:06:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鸣…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.66,0:06:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己说出来然后自己觉得痛苦 你还真是没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.31,0:06:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是 雪集也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.92,0:06:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.48,0:06:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤见子…!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.38,0:06:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.13,0:06:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾经好想…变得跟芽间一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.67,0:06:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.91,0:06:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 仁碳你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.95,0:07:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢芽间…吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.87,0:07:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是没用那种话去挑明…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.22,0:07:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁…谁会喜欢这种丑八怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.04,0:07:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.97,0:07:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.24,0:07:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…也不会变成那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.75,0:07:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.14,0:07:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鸣…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青蛙叫了就要回家～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青蛙叫了就要…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间 要回到哪里去才好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.86,0:08:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您想找什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.03,0:08:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.47,0:08:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.33,0:08:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥?「裤袋妖怪」?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.17,0:08:42.49,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}名字改自「口袋妖怪（ポケモン）」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.06,0:08:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还对客人要买的东西有意见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.65,0:08:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要哪一代的啊?「蛋白石」还是「绿宝石」?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.40,0:08:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「金」…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.41,0:08:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥?「裤袋妖怪·金」?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.07,0:08:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那都多少年前的东西了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.52,0:09:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 有的话就卖给我! 而且赶紧的!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.14,0:09:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎? 稀有裤袋妖怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错 芽间不是超想要的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.61,0:09:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她一直找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.51,0:09:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么一说 她还真是提过「建筑工」之类的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.90,0:09:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就肯定是啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.83,0:09:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4571日元
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.95,0:09:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五年前出的游戏 这定价也太暴利了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可要说清楚了 这是良心价啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.10,0:09:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为基本已经买不到了 所以要卖贵点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.82,0:09:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.17,0:09:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.50,0:09:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说宿海…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.08,0:09:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事了!多谢惠顾!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.41,0:09:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来啦 仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.04,0:09:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.43,0:10:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我在工作室烧制成功了一个颇赞的盘子 所以晚饭吃烤肉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.40,0:10:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我没食欲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算啥啊 一点都不可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎么弄来着…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.50,0:10:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从最初的三只里面选一只…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.55,0:10:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间还没回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.99,0:10:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的压力实体化形成的 我的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.13,0:10:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来就是不应该存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.91,0:10:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.67,0:10:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.93,0:11:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.10,0:11:18.02,title_no,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(266,510)}第二集
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.10,0:11:18.02,title_text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(323,598)}勇者芽间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.25,0:11:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.73,0:11:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.93,0:11:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.72,0:11:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.58,0:11:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久川
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.65,0:11:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像以前那样叫我波波就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.38,0:11:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真冷淡呢 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.09,0:11:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次有人用那种称呼叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.34,0:11:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意啦 说起来雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.36,0:11:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.40,0:11:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间在仁碳那里复活了的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.75,0:11:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 到现在还…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.77,0:11:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.71,0:11:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.74,0:12:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海是怎么说芽间的事情的?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.16,0:12:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 仁碳 那么久没见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.39,0:12:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙还是一如既往地强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.01,0:12:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海是怎么说芽间的事情的?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.94,0:12:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…幻听? 还是幻想来着?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.30,0:12:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间好像请他来实现愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.00,0:12:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 半路睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.05,0:12:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.95,0:12:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.18,0:12:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.31,0:12:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你怎么去洗澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.16,0:12:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸还没出门呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.55,0:12:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 总觉得洗澡的时候身上冷冷的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.57,0:12:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间最讨厌那样了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.89,0:13:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.50,0:13:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊 也给我稍微注意一下自己的成长…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.35,0:13:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 某部分好像没怎么成长就是了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.42,0:13:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某部分?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.44,0:13:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先给我把衣服穿上!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.60,0:13:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.76,0:13:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎? 好像是在哪里见过的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好 好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 难道是波波君? 好大块头呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.97,0:13:33.13,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}成长期真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.53,0:13:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.24,0:13:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和朋友交换?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.23,0:13:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是 听说用数据线和朋友交换裤袋妖怪的话就能拿到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.24,0:13:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 肉太美味了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.76,0:13:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚剩下的而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.95,0:13:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那叔叔就去上班了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.50,0:13:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一鲁粥…一路走好～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.74,0:14:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 我都忘得一干二净了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.71,0:14:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢 芽间也说过如果不是大家一起的话就实现不了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.36,0:14:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.10,0:14:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊波波 你是怎么想起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.29,0:14:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雪…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.44,0:14:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么说呢 我也看到幻听了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.43,0:14:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻听是看不到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,0:14:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.56,0:14:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.22,0:14:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说 只要再多弄到一个「裤袋妖怪」的游戏软件
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.93,0:14:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后再选一个不同的妖怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.96,0:14:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 很可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.07,0:14:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时最讨厌自己的卷发和眼镜了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.02,0:14:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对拥有光滑柔顺长发的芽间…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.61,0:14:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被仁碳所喜欢的芽间…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.43,0:14:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鸣 我们来贴配对的贴纸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.14,0:14:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.21,0:14:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 这个很可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.40,0:14:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也给安鸣一个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.73,0:15:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞定!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.32,0:15:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.41,0:15:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明很喜欢芽间 却又很讨厌她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.47,0:15:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣子 有时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.45,0:15:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真会使唤人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.57,0:15:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.80,0:15:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这里吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.66,0:15:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.48,0:15:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 安鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.78,0:15:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么嘛 我也要玩「裤袋妖怪」? 这不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.61,0:15:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔玩一下有什么问题嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.33,0:15:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就当寻找童真好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.82,0:15:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.47,0:15:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.58,0:15:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 眼镜呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.73,0:15:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你很烦啊 不戴又没什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:15:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请喝茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.59,0:16:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.36,0:16:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 你们两个也好久没来过了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.78,0:16:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚鸣子做的果冻要吃么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.38,0:16:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 安鸣的果冻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.92,0:16:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要用那种称呼叫我!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.80,0:16:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 芽间的愿望就是那个稀有裤袋妖怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.43,0:16:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 别说出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.98,0:16:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.25,0:16:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鸣?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.05,0:16:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没啥 芽间怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.73,0:16:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说是她托梦给我…之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.82,0:16:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…「裤袋妖怪」…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.44,0:16:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.50,0:16:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是 那里是「LOVE AND PERRY」的卡片
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.50,0:16:39.11,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}恶搞世嘉卡片式游戏「时尚魔女 LOVE AND BERRY」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.29,0:16:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是「猛牛王者」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:42.81,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}「猛牛王者」吗 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.82,0:16:45.35,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}要找的不是「猛牛王者」 是「裤袋妖怪」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.45,0:16:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么从刚才开始 你一直都不过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 有芽间在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.33,0:16:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈和安鸣都会很难过的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.06,0:16:53.90,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}「呆呆妖怪」也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.91,0:16:54.78,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}你说「呆呆妖怪」啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.79,0:16:55.96,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}那和电视里放的也有点不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.97,0:16:56.74,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.05,0:16:58.34,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}但是我们要找的是「裤袋妖怪」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.36,0:17:00.54,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}对了 「裤袋妖怪」「裤袋妖怪」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:01.65,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}你到底有没在找啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.68,0:17:04.39,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}当然有了 你才是有没好好地找
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.91,0:17:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那边坐下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.40,0:17:06.00,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}肯定在找啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.69,0:17:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 「BO☆BO-BO」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.40,0:17:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:11.88,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(181,188)}安城鸣子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:11.88,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(160,153)}名字：
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.24,0:17:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这种小小的游戏软件还要贴个名字 你还真是一丝不苟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.32,0:17:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.35,0:17:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没看「BO☆BO-BO」了 真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是难以置信 为啥没有泡伊特怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.33,0:17:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稀有裤袋妖怪不是要用泡伊山怪和袋鼠怪去交换吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.94,0:17:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野外是没有泡伊山怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.07,0:17:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用泡伊特进化才行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.18,0:17:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.06,0:17:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鸣…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.55,0:17:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.10,0:17:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 安鸣还是没变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.94,0:18:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很温柔 有很多漫画和游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.87,0:18:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是和那时一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.66,0:18:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.45,0:18:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种情景…总觉得好久没见过了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.06,0:18:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高兴…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.61,0:18:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.85,0:18:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 泡伊山怪出现了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.70,0:18:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 仁碳!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.59,0:18:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.61,0:18:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了 安城
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.72,0:18:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也…也没什么啦 消磨时间而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.08,0:19:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮助你的报酬 有么?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要钱的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.25,0:19:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.79,0:19:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来学校…上课吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.79,0:19:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.10,0:19:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还…还差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.23,0:19:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来只要连上数据线
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.18,0:19:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 这就可以和朋友进行交换了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安城?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.04,0:19:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 稍等
